quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  7,130,"Mpe tosilaki kozuisa bato ya falo mibu na mibu ebele na bozangi, na bokutuami ya bambuma mpo bakoka kokanisa"
  7,131,"Mpe soki bolamu ezui bango balobñoyo ewuti na biso, mpe soki mpasi ezui bango balobi: Bótala Mûssa na baye bazali naye, ya sólo, maye manso mazuaki bango ewutaki sé epaiya Allah, kasi ebele na bango bazali koyeba te"
  7,132,"Mpe balobi: Ata soki oyeli biso likamwisi, tokondimela na biso yo te"
  7,133,"Мре totindelaki bango pela ya mbula ya makasi, na mabanki na basili na magbololo mpe na makila, lokola bilembo bia polele. Kasi basalaki lolendo mpe bazalaki batomboki"
  7,134,"Mpe tango etumbu ekwelaki bango, balobi: Oh Mûssa! Sengela biso epai ya Nkolo wayo na maye apesaki yo elaka, soki alongoleli biso etumbu eye, tokondimela yo, mpe tokotikela yo bana na isalayele bökende elongo"
  7,135,"Mpe tango tolongoleli bango etumbu na eleko eye eyebanaki, bango wana bazangi botosi na elaka"
  7,136,"Mpe tosilikelaki bango mpe tozindisaki bango okati ya mayi mpo baboyaki kondima na bilembo bia biso, mpe bazalaki kotiya bokebi na yango te"
  7,137,"Mpe tokitanisaki bato oyo bazalaki na bolembu moniele ya mabele na eloli na yango miye topambolaki mpe elaka elamu ya Nkolo wayo ekokakiтропа bana ya isalayele тропа maye bakangaki mitema. Mpe tobebisaki maye falo na bato naye bazalaki kosala, mpe kotonga"
  7,138,"Mpe tokatisaki bana ba isalayele ebale mpe balekaki pene ya bato bazalaki kobondela bikeko. Mpe balobi: Oh Mûssa! Šalela biso nzambe lokola oyo ya bango. Alobi: Ya soló, bozali bato ya boyinga"
  7,139,"Ya sólo, baye wana, maye bazali kobondela ezali mabe, mpe nyoso bazali kosala ezali na ntina te (ezanga litomba)"
  7,140,"Alobi: Nalukela bino nzambe mosusu oyo azali Allah te mpe ye atomboli bino o kati ya mikili(otango na bango) koleka bato banso"
  7,141,"(Bokanisa) tango tobikisaki bino na etumbu ya falo, bazalaki koboma bana na bino ya mibali mpe bazali kotika basi ba bino. Mpe wana ezali momekano monene kowuta epai ya Nkolo wa bino"